data.description: This spacious 3 Sided brick beauty is awaiting a new owner. This 5 large bedroom 4 full bath home sits in a Tranquil Snellville community. This beauty opens into a foyer featuring hardwood flooring w/sep LR/DR. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a designer backsplash, an island, and a kitchen bar with a breakfast area. The sunken family room w/rear stairs leading to the owner's suite is a must-have! 1 Bedroom on the main level w/full bath is perfect for an in-law suite/guest room for private quarters. The laundry room is located on the main floor. The oversized owner's suite features a sitting room for relaxing and a walk-in closet. 3 Spacious secondary bedrooms on the second floor are perfect for everyone to spread out, and the backyard is unexpectedly large, great for entertaining. Schedule your tour today!
